OL,3,CCCTV appeal after 'fare dodging
OL,4,Cpassenger spits in rail worker's face'
OL,6,FPolice want to speak to a woman seen
OL,7,Fon CCTV after a passenger who did not
OL,8,Fpay their fare spat in the face of a
OL,9,Frail worker in Ilford.
OL,11,FOfficers said a woman went through the
OL,12,Fbarriers without a ticket and
OL,13,Fassaulted a member of staff when
OL,14,Fchallenged.
OL,16,FShe then quickly left the station.
OL,18,FBritish Transport Police said:
OL,19,F"Officers believe the woman in the
OL,20,Fimages could have information that may
OL,21,Fassist their ongoing investigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/2
