OL,3,CCCTV appeal after 'fare dodging
OL,4,Cpassenger spits in rail worker's face'
OL,6,F"Anyone who recognises her is asked to
OL,7,Fcontact BTP by texting BTP on 61016 or
OL,8,Fcalling 0800 40 50 40, using the
OL,9,Freference 530 of 22 May.
OL,11,F"Information can be given anonymously
OL,12,Fto Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111."
